***REMOVED*** Google ADK Configuration
***REMOVED*** Copy to .env and fill in your values

***REMOVED*** =============================================================================
***REMOVED*** Model Selection
***REMOVED*** =============================================================================

***REMOVED*** Default model for ADK agents (options: gemini-2.5-flash, gemini-2.5-pro, gemini-3-pro)
ADK_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash

***REMOVED*** =============================================================================
***REMOVED*** Google AI / Gemini
***REMOVED*** =============================================================================

***REMOVED*** Google AI API Key (for Gemini via AI Studio)
***REMOVED*** Get from: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
GOOGLE_GENAI_API_KEY=

***REMOVED*** =============================================================================
***REMOVED*** Vertex AI (Enterprise/Production)
***REMOVED*** =============================================================================

***REMOVED*** Google Cloud Project ID
VERTEX_AI_PROJECT_ID=

***REMOVED*** Vertex AI Location (e.g., us-central1, europe-west1)
VERTEX_AI_LOCATION=us-central1

***REMOVED*** Path to service account key (optional, uses ADC if not set)
GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS=

***REMOVED*** =============================================================================
***REMOVED*** Backend API
***REMOVED*** =============================================================================

***REMOVED*** Backend API base URL
API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000/api

***REMOVED*** =============================================================================
***REMOVED*** Alternative Models (Optional)
***REMOVED*** =============================================================================

***REMOVED*** For multi-model support, you can configure:
***REMOVED*** - Claude via Anthropic API
***REMOVED*** - GPT via OpenAI API

***REMOVED*** Anthropic API Key (for Claude fallback)
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

***REMOVED*** OpenAI API Key (for GPT fallback)
OPENAI_API_KEY=
